  "subject": "feat: ArgoCD source-hydrator bootstrap, scoped AppProject, datalake-kind app",
  "body": "Pins argo/argo-cd chart 10.1.3 (newest published chart at execution time)\nwith global.image.tag=v3.5.0-rc2 override: no argo-helm chart bundles\nArgoCD >=v3.5 yet (GA hasn't shipped, only rc1/rc2), and the Source\nHydrator needs the v3.5 beta-stability line (timeout/requeue fixes) per\nthe GAUGE report's floor. commitServer.enabled is confirmed as the\ncorrect values key for this chart version.\n\nAppProject datalake is scoped to the repo + the five Helm chart repos\nthis platform will use; Application datalake-kind hydrates chart/ to\nbranch environments/kind via the commit-server, using a write-capable\nrepo credential so the hydrator can push rendered manifests.\n"
}
